description:
We are a community focused around the Angel Beats! anime, visual novel and mangas, as well as discussing common interests! We hope that you enjoy your time here and meet a lot of cool people! Please take some time to read through our rules and info below. Thank you! <:YuriHappy:561738291083214873>

:small_blue_diamond: **New to the series?**
Find out more on these links: 
[MAL](https://myanimelist.net/anime/6547/Angel_Beats) | [AniList](https://anilist.co/anime/6547/Angel-Beats/) | [ANN](https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=10885) | [Kitsu](https://kitsu.io/anime/angel-beats) | [AniDB](https://anidb.net/anime/6564) | [Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angel_Beats!) | [Wikia/Fandom](https://angelbeats.fandom.com/) | [Subreddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/AngelBeats/)

> _"One person needed courage to face the past. Another person needed effort to make a dream come true. Yet another person needed time and friends. What about you?"_ 
- Yuzuru Otonashi
